    <script>
        const correctAnswer = "cake";
        function checkAnswer() {
        const userInput = document.getElementById("answer").value.toLowerCase();
        if (userInput.includes(correctAnswer)) {
            showCard();
        } else {
            alert("Oops! Try again with a birthday-themed answer!");
        }
        }
        function showCard() {
        document.getElementById("questionCard").classList.add("hidden");
        document.getElementById("ecard").classList.remove("hidden");
        const base64Image = "data:image/jpeg;base64,"; // Paste base64 image string here
        const imgEl = document.getElementById("photoPreview");
        if (base64Image) {
            imgEl.src = base64Image;
            imgEl.classList.remove("hidden");
        } else {
            imgEl.classList.add("hidden");
        }
        launchEffects();
        }
        function launchEffects() {
        for (let i = 0; i < 40; i++) {
            const confetti = document.createElement('div');
            confetti.classList.add('confetti');
            confetti.style.left = Math.random() * 100 + 'vw';
            confetti.style.backgroundColor = ['#ff8aa2', '#ffd166', '#70d6ff'][i % 3];
            confetti.style.animationDuration = (3 + Math.random() * 2) + 's';
            document.body.appendChild(confetti);
            setTimeout(() => confetti.remove(), 5000);
        }
        for (let i = 0; i < 20; i++) {
            const sparkle = document.createElement('div');
            sparkle.classList.add('sparkle');
            sparkle.style.left = Math.random() * 100 + 'vw';
            sparkle.style.top = Math.random() * 100 + 'vh';
            sparkle.style.animationDelay = `${Math.random() * 2}s`;
            document.body.appendChild(sparkle);
        }
        }
    </script>
